data.description: Welcome to the highly desired Seagate Village, a community with a rich history as part of the Myrtle Beach Air Force Base. The neighborhood exudes a nostalgic charm, boasting mature trees and inviting sidewalks. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers an expansive front yard and a lengthy driveway leading to a covered carport offering an escape unlike others in the neighborhood. Walking into the kitchen you'll notice stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a subway tile backsplash. Walking further into this 2 bedroom 1 bathroom all brick home you'll enjoy plantation shutters and wood parquet flooring. An array of activities awaits you in the vicinity, conveniently accessible by a golf cart ride. Indulge in the shopping and dining offerings in the Market Common area. Schedule your showing today!
